&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product and Operations to address onboarding friction and improve customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide structured market feedback to influence pricing, offering, and go-to-market strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
