&lt;li&gt;One of our &lt;strong&gt;fastest-growing categories&lt;/strong&gt;, mainly smart home, TV and audio, with exposure across the wider portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sourcing stock at the right price: your first 90 days are about finding available inventory while hitting a &lt;strong&gt;15–20% discount vs RRP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The procurement strategy behind your categories, plus access to trade fairs and industry events as we bring new products on board&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
