&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong negotiation and communication skills&lt;/strong&gt;: you&#39;re comfortable talking directly with suppliers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An analytical mindset&lt;/strong&gt;, confident working with data and spreadsheets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of &lt;strong&gt;consumer electronics categories&lt;/strong&gt; (mobile, audio, smart home, TV) is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fluent English&lt;/strong&gt;; another European language is a bonus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organised and detail-oriented&lt;/strong&gt;: you can manage multiple workstreams at once&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;registered freelance setup&lt;/strong&gt; that allows you to work with clients in Germany&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
