&lt;li&gt;Brand and campaign copy - from big-idea concepts and taglines to headlines, scripts, and long-form storytelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance and growth copy for paid social, display, search, and landing pages - with a clear understanding of how words drive conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CRM and lifecycle copy across email, push, and in-app messaging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product copy support on web, app, and checkout surfaces, partnering with Product, Design, and Engineering through Contentful&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grover&#39;s AI copy stack: prompts, brand-voice style guides, and workflows in Gemini, Claude, Lokalise, and Contentful so other teams can self-serve high-quality copy at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🤝 What you bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience as a copywriter in a fast-paced environment (agency, scale-up, or in-house brand team)&lt;/li&gt;
