&lt;li&gt;A portfolio that shows range and craft: brand and campaign work, performance copy that converts, and lifecycle copy that builds relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience using AI tools (Gemini, Claude, or equivalent) as part of your daily craft - from ideation and first drafts to localization and QA&lt;/li&gt;
