&lt;p&gt;You’ll join our Product team at our Berlin HQ (3 days per week, Tuesday to Thursday), reporting into our Director of Product and working day to day with CRM and lifecycle marketing, engineering, design, and data, with regular exposure to senior leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
