&lt;li&gt;Shape an engaging experience that grows customer lifetime value and reduces revocation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and drive the KPIs that define success, such as Multi-Sub Adoption Rate, mobile app engagement, churn and revocation rate, and customer lifetime value (CLV), treating them as a connected system rather than a scorecard.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive product discovery through A/B testing, user research, and deep data analysis to understand what renters actually need and find new opportunities for engagement and growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate the real trade-offs between growth and credit risk, partnering with CRM and lifecycle marketers, engineers, designers, and data analysts, and communicating strategy, priorities, and results clearly to senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
