&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🎯&amp;nbsp; What you will contribute:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take charge of Google Ads (Search, Display, YouTube, Shopping) and Meta campaigns, optimizing for both web and app performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, test, and iterate data-driven strategies to improve effectiveness and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage cross-channel budgets, balancing spending efficiency with campaign impact and scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with BI, Risk and Purchasing to leverage insights for continuous portfolio, audience and performance improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with external partners, such as marketing platforms, feed management, agencies and managed services to expand campaign capabilities and drive innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work alongside brand, product, and category teams to ensure cohesive marketing efforts and to enhance conversion rates along the funnel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date on emerging features in Google Ads, Paid Social platforms, and other performance marketing tools to ensure best practices and state-of-the-art campaign management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;🤝 What you bring:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
